room_title: Escape room "Western Renegades" by Extreme Escape Redding in Redding
room_description:
You have been locked away by the Sheriff who believes you are guilty of the multiple recent stagecoach robberies. You know you're innocent so you must clear your name. You have 60 minutes to free yourself from your partner, your cell, and your room.
Upon escape, you will be confronted by the Sheriff and must give him your evidence proving who actually committed the crime and their current location. The bandit is already on the move so you have to work quickly. Otherwise, the Sherrif will through you back in the clink and lock you away for good!
